        "answer": "Capsa Capital Partners' official website is https://www.capsa-capital.com/en/index.html. It is a private equity firm based in Tunisia.\nCapsa Capital Partners is a venture capital and private equity firm based in Tunis. Capsa AI is a technology company founded in 2023, specializing in AI for private capital. Capsa AI automates investment tasks to enhance efficiency and decision-making.\nCapsa Capital Partners is a London-based AI operating system for private capital, raised $18 million in Series A funding in 2026. Investors include TX Ventures, Pivot Investment Partners, and Bek Ventures. Founded in 2023, it aims to streamline private capital workflows.\nCapsa Capital Partners is a private equity firm founded in 2012 in Tunisia. It manages funds for institutional investors and focuses on sectors like agriculture and technology. Capsa AI, a separate entity, raised $18 million in Series A funding in 2026.\nCapsa Capital Partners is a private equity firm focused on supporting small and medium enterprises in Tunisia. Capsa AI raised $18 million in Series A funding to develop an AI operating system for private capital. Capsa Healthcare acquired MASS Medical, expanding its healthcare product offerings.",
